sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant M as Miragic AI
    participant D as DB
    U->>F: Upload human+cloth images
    F->>B: POST /api/tryon/single
    B->>M: POST /virtual-try-on
    M-->>B: jobId
    loop Poll 10s
        B->>M: GET /job/{jobId}
    end
    M-->>B: resultImageUrl
    B-->>F: {processedUrl}
    F-->>U: Display result
    B->>D: Save history
